大违规查处力度，确保高考公平公正。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-1f655acfa5fca0fac5fdbfecaa2f9750_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/531770848"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip4+x89OWgt8OEAMaCDgwNDUzNDA3IMWJ2ZMGMAk4oQFALHIJNTMxNzcwODQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1651946791.0046945", "card_id": "Q_531736383", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "斯里兰卡第二次宣布进入紧急状态，原因是什么？将会如何发展？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "斯里兰卡总统戈塔巴雅·拉贾帕克萨当地时间 5 月 6 日宣布，从当天午夜起该国全国进入公共紧急状态，以维持社会秩序。 这是该国在五周之内第二次进入紧急状态。由于斯里兰卡面临外汇匮乏、物资短缺、物价高涨、供电紧张等问题，各地爆发了抗议及罢工行动。总统戈塔巴雅·拉贾帕克萨 4 月 1 日曾宣布该国进入公共紧急状态，并于 4 月 5 日午夜取消了这一状态。（央视新闻）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-cc4316bacf85146ae3784e956fadeb44_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/531736383"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIp4+x89OWgt8OEAMaCDgwNDQ1NzM2IK+U2JMGMAI4OEAtcgk1MzE3MzYzODN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1651946791.0053651", "card_id": "Q_525647461", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "比亚迪为什么不出一款对标理想 one 的车？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是因为比亚迪没有这个产品力吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-0b74198dfc695b8ad2b5e7299b23026d_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/525647461"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ip4+x89OWgt8OEAMaCDc5MDkyMjM2ILTYoJIGMAE4OkAucgk1MjU2NDc0NjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_165